Rating: 0
for those who want the caramel filling, the caramel liquid must be added EXQUISITELY slowly in order for it not to seize(harden and not combine) when hitting the yolk/cream mixture. If some caramel does seize, you can relax it by putting mixture back over low heat and slowly it will melt and combine with the rest of the mixture. it is a delicious filling.

